      {
        "id": "68bb0948-5e25-485e-81e1-9a1a7f2c1e92",
        "type": "nodetool.text.Prompt",
        "data": {
          "prompt": "Cinematic {{ genre }} movie poster, theatrical one-sheet.\n\nScene: {{ scene }}\nCore visual concept: {{ core_visual_concept }}\nArt direction: {{ design }}\n\nA single hero subject dominates the frame with strong visual hierarchy, dramatic cinematic lighting, and rich depth. The movie title \"{{ title }}\" is set large across the lower third in premium typography that matches the art direction, with a short tagline above it. A bottom billing block carries credits, studio logos, and a release date in authentic Hollywood layout. Balanced negative space, poster-grade composition, award-winning key art."
        },
        "ui_properties": {
          "selected": false,
          "position": {
            "x": 2148,
            "y": 169
          },
          "zIndex": 0,
          "width": 410,
          "height": 555,
          "title": "Compose poster image prompt",
          "selectable": true,
          "bypassed": false
        },
        "dynamic_properties": {
          "title": "",
          "genre": "",
          "design": "",
          "core_visual_concept": "",
          "scene": ""
        },
        "dynamic_outputs": {}
      },
      {
        "id": "923fb0f1-8bd4-406a-ba73-9ec3137c20cd",
        "type": "nodetool.text.Prompt",
        "data": {
          "prompt": "You are pitching poster concepts for the film \"{{ title }}\" ({{ genre }}).\n\nPositioning: {{ positioning }}\nAudience insight: {{ audience_insight }}\n\nGenerate distinct theatrical poster concepts. Each concept is ONE self-contained line describing a single striking image: the hero subject, the setting, the framing, and the mood. Vary the ideas across the set — different angles, symbols, and emotional beats — while staying true to the genre and positioning. One concept per line, no numbering and no commentary."
        },
        "ui_properties": {
          "selected": false,
